GSD.description:
net/sched: sch_taprio: fix possible use-after-free

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.1.9 by commit d3b2d2820a005e43855fa71b80c4a4b194201c60, it was introduced in version v4.20 by commit 5a781ccbd19e4664babcbe4b4ead7aa2b9283d22. For more details please see the references link.
